data.title: City of Los Angeles Department of Recreation and Parks
data.text: Many large, beautiful parks are located within the City's boundaries and are operated and maintained by the Los Angeles City Recreation and Parks Department. Department property which includes AQUATIC CENTERS, RECREATION CENTERS , PRE-SCHOOL AGE LICENSE CHILD CARE CENTERS , SENIOR CITIZEN CENTERS and other centers are listed in those respective areas of this site. Many of our recreation centers have picnic areas, sports fields, and other park features. Locations listed below are those without recreation or other centers on the premises. Other park listings include: DOG PARKS and SKATE PARKS .
